xt-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-82f93db6-8651-4cd7-940f-7cb95bd6e275\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-42a08b2a-daf7-46cf-817b-e5954ef3d62f\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">요구분석 중간에</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0cdf2653-de3d-46b4-9fff-bb5733e26467\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3ca07d55-3ca7-4e07-a706-0406851edc11\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>톤 앤 매너 디자인 작업이</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e0c3aeef-db40-4c35-a3bc-e41f45945261\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> 진행됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-03fe0cb2-2913-4525-bd7b-04d88fbf9ec4\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2690a4d6-cb53-4778-bc13-cdf2e6ee7514\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">대부분의 업체는 메인페이지나 기본 디자인을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-62101a7d-5048-4b00-9a7c-23ccfb6b1b8d\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6c67de34-2237-4379-a8dd-08fda831f635\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">변경하는 요구를 하게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1ce8c215-ce97-4b70-8027-3951d6f119de\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-37003946-24ad-4262-963d-f3f155513676\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">이럴 때 업체에 맞는 기본 스타일 가이드를</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9ddbefe7-9797-4816-bd2b-57bf3f37dcdb\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-dc50245c-ffcb-42e6-949a-e54a3b40fd69\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">제작하여 컨펌을 받게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b9915623-6e83-4e75-b1f0-e3c09ec62bc3\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-60468df8-5346-40e1-8801-ed8fe21282ac\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">이 톤 앤 매너가 통과되면</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6900b356-92df-43fa-bb80-0abc709e4dee\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-39a4ada1-3c28-409f-a0c0-35d6cb4fdd41\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">기본적인 5가지 페이지를</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-30058b3e-07f5-4845-999d-ad07d441bd61\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c075f168-d70e-462a-bc1b-51cae105acd2\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">통일된 디자인으로 살을 붙이게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1beecdd0-60c9-42c8-bbd3-c77bc6d0270a\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5bfb72e3-8d74-49cf-b71e-41f836620e60\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">기본적인 5가지는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-594dee3c-ad3f-4e69-a2e7-851fea16120a\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-da0d7413-a248-4c1e-ada4-26500f9dc151\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>메인페이지</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7bf2d702-1e8a-450b-af27-ec0bc49faf1e\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ea3169a7-1308-4211-901c-08efb81ff39c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>주문페이지</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-10a0e773-56cc-41a6-9d14-66a6189a9386\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-442be41c-0fda-4b1e-ab48-2bdb55d21351\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>마이페이지</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-746b0c1b-9cb9-4b7c-ade6-854bdc9bcb88\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f6fdef15-1e90-46af-9e91-ccf4aa411852\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>콘텐츠페이지</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-57b9428a-9e80-48c4-ae44-b35e26ec1862\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-961295d8-7f7b-4608-b07e-afac54eca623\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>기타</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-05211a14-9ed6-41ee-941a-50268542a5a3\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5c92c6b8-be4a-47da-b1b1-3d6400286b8f\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-429623b0-ded0-41ee-8da9-4f5772939326\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">이 5가지 기본에 살을 붙은 후</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-71ce0db8-032a-42a5-a6a0-d65b95c32eb6\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-902ca9f3-2816-4029-9ab1-137b53ecf80b\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>백엔드 작업</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-012d2e95-797a-49a7-9eac-5d1de0447539\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">을 하게 되며</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-028a47ba-8622-4c3d-a1e6-612980c0e2f4\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2d18970a-0215-4369-9c4c-360719fffc6a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">백엔드 작업이 완료되면</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2dd38ab6-45f6-496e-9703-9a5f8124d2a6\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6137875d-0c9f-467f-bfc4-afc780176cc3\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">하나하나 테스트 과정을 통해</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-993e6f07-81d1-44a4-836b-6653bb10af34\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1515297c-5942-41be-a12b-76b7d66ceb33\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">검증의 절차를 가지게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a818f673-f3f4-48a5-bc42-7a1ae121d9a8\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-29e4de60-2e43-4926-bd50-4dcb0d3fb0dd\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">기존의 사이트가 있다면</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-49ef3e78-c45b-4ecb-9f65-a92b616bb068\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ce92b94c-e421-4a3a-9702-12186823143b\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>마이그레이션 기본 작업이</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c49dfc33-c0ce-4f07-9345-6b25adfb58d6\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7cbef7c8-764d-43ef-91f7-f7ba4d65eadd\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">진행되고 없다면 약 1~2달에 걸친</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-84e7cb34-54b2-4b5d-a5a7-fc46cb402d8c\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-67aad2ee-399c-4d1c-a21a-85c5bbaaeafd\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">테스팅이 진행되면서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c2334c66-265d-41cd-b239-ef07f0bf21b4\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-128a0fe7-1cd2-4b19-8f26-06a2bcc8c64c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">수정 작업을 거치게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9ec48cbb-da26-43fb-a0aa-09e5e66433f7\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-519a4aeb-f871-4c85-9fcc-a5d9ede53be2\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">수정이 어느 정도 완성되면</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e8168bc0-3c1e-4b1b-b7fa-0a71ea7fdd1d\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a7083ff4-2f4f-47f3-a998-4bf4a8ae6749\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>베타 오픈을</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a6201133-6bb4-45a7-bac8-71e205749c2d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> 통해 마케팅과 베타테스트가</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2503b562-735f-40b5-b95c-a4d7f164d55c\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-cf852f50-9087-4de6-9dca-743ab7078672\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">진행되고 이후 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-58c0f980-020a-4429-810c-ebc89f2f78f2\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>그랜드 오픈 과정을</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-010022d2-3d1b-4f02-b3d3-4749008b4264\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> 거칩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e8a60e3d-bb8b-4432-89df-ad17a7a161ab\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-0e642169-1fe2-4df9-8953-e6f0cf9a5430\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">이후 발생되는 수정 보안은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-64bc8d76-0a14-436e-9326-549707fb2567\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-82cc026e-a575-41cf-8dc0-ea2c82d99035\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">유지 보수 계약과 버그 작업의</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6581ce90-53ed-480d-b8e2-a9d0ebe9ccde\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5e3bfead-c8f9-4e2a-b58c-216a10a7ff11\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">수정이 이루어지면서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2030344e-0af0-48c8-9517-397b2e322b5d\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d881e68b-29a4-40a3-851d-8a3512fd3190\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>사이트가 점점 완성</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e1c53ee8-ef7c-4405-afbb-d5d0b4772672\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">되게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3b69482e-fab3-4074-a50d-c104d0dbab87\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e05146b0-54b3-4bb5-a96e-bd808d6c8787\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-table se-l-table_layout1\" id=\"SE-e1863edd-d735-439c-9982-444755c6b5c2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-table se-l-table_layout1 se-section-align-\" style=\"width: 42%;\">\n<div class=\"se-table-container\">\n<table class=\"se-table-content\" style=\"border-style:solid;border-width:1px 0px 0px 1px;border-color:#00b3f2;\">\n<tbody><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 100.0%; height: 255.0px; border-style:solid;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-color:#00b3f2; background-color: #f7f7f7;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1e19c688-fa31-499e-acc2-31a1b9fe5cad\" style=\"line-height:2.3;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-d53c5643-8e06-491d-9a15-74d6cd417f80\" style=\"\"><b> </b></span><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-cf84ee21-fe53-4fe3-9c92-966799dc0229\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b> </b></span><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanummyeongjo\" id=\"SE-88fb1661-b919-4a82-a19e-335d3cb57dbc\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b> 사이트 사용자 페이지 매뉴얼  v1.0 ::</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummyeongjo se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-0426a3a9-f088-4061-91f0-3e15c46e6d47\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>:</b></span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b4dabbe4-7d58-4f45-8c67-68433a415c41\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-1c546d6f-baf4-477c-8426-0d139e963339\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"> </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs34 se-ff-nanummyeongjo\" id=\"SE-c05b0cee-67e4-4723-b0bc-c8a8710aebd4\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b> 사이트</b></span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-40c52253-a84d-4873-aece-ca44b939f5a8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs34 se-ff-nanummyeongjo\" id=\"SE-a4237830-fbc3-4051-86a3-d10158d8dcd5\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>   개발 진행 과정</b></span></p></div>\n</td></tr></tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-1f07239f-f974-4427-ba47-68f691adeae4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223614798227/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d6c73ce7-4daf-426e-8c40-870b0ba7d23d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs38 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f7a95f77-3ccb-488b-bdce-fbdf1f8d00e5\" style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>요구분석</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6d7bad9f-5064-47a4-92b9-e8b255c844e9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-58be29d9-a76a-4787-866e-3609cef761da\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">개발에서 큰 3단계는 기획 &gt; 개발 &gt; 테스트라고 할 수 있습니다. 그중에 기획 단계에서 가장 중요한 것이 요구분석입니다. 요구분석이란 클라이언트의 니즈(Needs)를 파악하여 그것을 정리하고 요약하여 사이트에 담아내는 작업입니다. 이 작업은 매우 중요합니다. 모든 사이트에서 실패한 경험이 있는 분이시라면 실패의 원인을 기획에서 찾는 분이 많습니다. 이는 개발 PM이 고객의 니즈를 담아내지 못했거나 또는 클라이언트의 변덕(?)이라고 불리는 액션 때문에 대부분 발생합니다. 개발사 입장에서는 클라이언트의 변덕(?) 만큼 힘든 부분이 없습니다. 이런 실패를 극복하기 위해 반드시 정확한 요구분석서를 작성하여 컨펌을 받고 추후에도 발생되는 수정 부분은 서로의 협의를 통해 조정해야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8e7d1656-9f26-4f27-b511-05493f64c515\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0a48fcb9-ba16-46bd-b025-9b4ac420a48b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f471cde9-60aa-40be-aebb-24a2acc30fdd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-dfb93410-f49a-410b-9593-6cda2daaffd1\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>컨셉과 벤치마킹</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7096ad25-093f-47a6-a03d-8dd103594c97\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e0ba4cc-2a2d-4646-a6e8-d13c4ca2dd5d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">사이트의 컨셉은 매우 중요합니다. 어떤 컨셉으로 개발하여 고객에게 내용을 전달할지를 정해야 합니다. 이 컨셉은 협의로 정할 수 있지만 가장 좋은 방법은 컨셉에 가장 잘 맞는 벤치마킹 사이트를 참고하는 방법입니다. 이 벤치마킹 사이트를 잘 잡으면 편하고 빠르게 개발할 수 있습니다. 저희는 단순한 주문 방식이 좋다! 또는 정확하고 자세히 정보를 알려주겠다! 또는 고객과의 소통 페이지가 가장 중요한 요소이다 등등입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-41327837-f57b-4435-bced-e9b0db2d65de\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223614798227/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-367cd637-901b-41f3-b178-b2ec891701cd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-5ea690f1-d933-4757-912c-832769aec005\" style=\"\">moo.com</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-59e62e70-e658-43fd-bd78-3b940a7e0e63\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223614798227/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b0e75a8b-cfef-4f34-84bc-8d9fd6654082\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-59d5124d-e57f-4a4a-a569-83e50d60aeb6\" style=\"\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://www.vistaprint.com/holiday/christmas-cards?keyword=full%20photo\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.vistaprint.com/holiday/christmas-cards?keyword=full%20photo</a></span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f605a2a6-939d-45b8-82df-21e4be4c3034\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-d989e6db-61b1-4132-9857-5e595be8662d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223614798227/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fa155cb4-40a7-44dc-b3e5-c70ce231ebdc\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs38 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-fa9b7040-f1dc-4e83-b455-57b6a94bf89d\" style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>톤 앤 매너</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9bb5856d-00ef-4a71-bc9a-b91044d3f9a1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-785e06c4-c334-4a59-b256-667cdd47ec26\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">프런트 개발에서 가장 중요한 것은 요구분석에 따른 고객의 성향을 판단하여 디자인 가이드를 잡는 일입니다. 이는 로고의 색상일 수도 있고 형식일 수도 있으며 스타일일 수도 있습니다. 이를 위해 아이콘 형식과 주문방법에 따른 메뉴도 정리될 수 있습니다. 단순하게 만들거나 편리함을 추구하는 기능을 넣을 수도 있고 내용을 팝업 형태로 만 숨겨 보일 때 심플한 점을 부각시킬 수도 있습니다. 대부분 몇 개 업체의 잘 만든 벤치마킹 사이트를 추천하여 수정하고 작업하는 것이 일반적입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a456de6-2fe4-4e93-bf37-46c6a4caa582\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223614798227/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ecc3b3f8-ee14-4a86-a26d-abc452a1bfc5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223614798227/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e7ce1fbd-d117-4ab1-b265-646ea2d45906\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223614798227/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dc868203-848f-4bf9-9617-1b708ada0fe7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223614798227/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0dc0e346-cf74-40a9-9b9e-0a1534ffd4fd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-260f8d20-0e6c-445f-8537-0647c7ce2fef\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223614798227/009.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cfa237e5-7d8c-4525-8805-a9c1ffa4c1da\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs38 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f6a1d78d-f50b-469d-9e45-59d0e618b468\" style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>개발</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0a4b42e4-5661-47af-8050-46225af7c8e8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-641adab1-e8ac-4350-b0d7-c0a60d93f061\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">프런트의 디자인 컨셉이 조금씩 진행되면 관리자와의 연동 작업이 진행됩니다. 연동은 이미지 연동, 가격 연동, 시스템 등의 연동 등으로 나뉠 수 있습니다. 관리자에서 책정한 가격을 주문단에 붙이는 작업을 하게 됩니다. 사이트 정보 중에 가장 중요한 것은 가격입니다. 가격정보가 다르면 혼란과 영업에 차질을 발생시킬 수 있습니다. 기본적으로 저희 관리자에서는 가격을 엑셀로 업/다운로드할 수 있습니다. 하지만 대부분 모든 금액을 넣는 것을 어려워합니다. 이 부분을 수정하기 위해 기본가격에서 요율과 금액으로 조정하는 작업을 하게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-25718087-8f54-4dfe-be4d-8b9765742ecd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:583px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223614798227/010.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ba53d89a-d217-4c56-b891-647a27782813\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7ac5ba70-fa8f-4afe-9852-76eeabca4b4b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6948716e-dabb-4efb-9cd9-51d3fb34fe99\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">기존 가격을 정하고 적용률과 적용금액을 책정하여 단가를 확정합니다. 이 부분도 기본적으로 업체에 맞게 커스텀 개발을 해 드립니다. 기본은 기준가격을 정하고 자신이 *나 \\을 통해 수정하도록 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-456ff5d5-04f0-4dda-81d4-9ca9780001ff\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a839d58c-37b3-46a6-8a94-7086f6d155e1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f005f6f1-eff5-4c3c-8944-06383539071e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223614798227/011.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dd85d13b-dc87-4e7b-bf9a-bc1e7f9d3200\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-586ba241-3750-488e-b31d-694a0f95ed3e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-aceec7f3-2976-4849-a30c-d3e61b4d1f92\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">종이나 가타 요소들도 가격을 통해 수정해 완성합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f2f0bdd8-5289-41fb-ba30-24254a67783c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ff230718-3b5c-4cbb-af7c-beac47037bfe\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-66e13e15-63fe-4917-8f83-39e804ac3653\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-01e9ece7-5ffa-4bfa-9f2e-e57b6c4e5472\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-af6d0be6-13e8-43b2-98e3-b5e163d34826\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-03871898-c378-4ab3-8996-125e98a87c66\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-